<div xml:space="preserve">
<p begin="75000000t" end="128000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle0"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>为了一艘船 竟然离开了从东海一起走到这里的伙伴</b></font></p>
<p begin="139000000t" end="167000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>你们哭什么哭啊</b></font></p>
<p begin="167000000t" end="194000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle2"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>白痴 我们才没有哭呢 白痴</b></font></p>
<p begin="196000000t" end="249000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle3"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>不过你这样独自守护船 确实令我感动万分</b></font></p>
<p begin="250000000t" end="286000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle4"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>我们没哭 谁也没哭</b></font></p>
<p begin="286000000t" end="305000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle5"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>这些家伙有病啊</b></font></p>
<p begin="333000000t" end="350000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle6"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>总之这下你们清楚了吧</b></font></p>
<p begin="351000000t" end="382000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle7"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>我已经不是他们的伙伴了</b></font></p>
<p begin="393000000t" end="403000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle8"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>如此...</b></font></p>
<p begin="413000000t" end="432000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle9"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>如此悲伤 令我不得不高歌一曲</b></font></p>
<p begin="435000000t" end="461000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle10"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>歌名就叫“同伴离别 北风狂啸”</b></font></p>
<p begin="467000000t" end="483000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle11"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>大哥好帅</b></font></p>
<p begin="487000000t" end="508000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle12"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>你们当我是白痴吗</b></font></p>
<p begin="520000000t" end="532000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle13"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>大哥</b></font></p>
<p begin="568000000t" end="581000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle14"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>救命...</b></font></p>
<p begin="631000000t" end="666000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle15"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>你们的大哥就由我去跟他打声招呼吧</b></font></p>
<p begin="725000000t" end="738000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle16"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>知道地点了</b></font></p>
<p begin="746000000t" end="755000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle17"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>我们走</b></font></p>
<p begin="1011000000t" end="1033000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle18"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>小哥 我帮你沏了茶</b></font></p>
<p begin="1034000000t" end="1049000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle19"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>休息一下吧</b></font></p>
<p begin="1067000000t" end="1100000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle20"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>多谢了 修好这里我就去喝</b></font></p>
<p begin="1213000000t" end="1225000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle21"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>好疼啊</b></font></p>
<p begin="1226000000t" end="1250000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle22"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>好疼 疼死我了</b></font></p>
<p begin="1262000000t" end="1291000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle23"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>我说小哥啊</b></font></p>
<p begin="1305000000t" end="1324000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle24"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>我就直入正题吧</b></font></p>
<p begin="1326000000t" end="1352000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle25"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>你一直修船要做什么</b></font></p>
<p begin="1363000000t" end="1375000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle26"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>什么做什么啊</b></font></p>
<p begin="1375000000t" end="1396000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle27"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>那当然是要继续和它一起冒险</b></font></p>
<p begin="1396000000t" end="1428000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle28"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>总有一天 一定要回到我的故乡东海</b></font></p>
<p begin="1439000000t" end="1463000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle29"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>虽然可能无法环绕世界一圈</b></font></p>
<p begin="1465000000t" end="1487000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle30"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>但既然已经来过了伟大航路</b></font></p>
<p begin="1488000000t" end="1515000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle31"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>这足以让我凯旋而归了</b></font></p>
<p begin="1520000000t" end="1534000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle32"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>我可以昂首挺胸地...</b></font></p>
<p begin="1534000000t" end="1556000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle33"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>不 你回不去的</b></font></p>
<p begin="1566000000t" end="1614000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle34"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>东海实在太远了</b></font></p>
<p begin="1661000000t" end="1673000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle35"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>大哥...</b></font></p>
<p begin="1691000000t" end="1747000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle36"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>刚才将船吊上来的时候 我已经仔细观察过了</b></font></p>
<p begin="1757000000t" end="1786000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle37"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>你们快住手 想把梅利怎么样啊</b></font></p>
<p begin="1786000000t" end="1818000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle38"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>给我把绳子解开 放下船</b></font></p>
<p begin="1821000000t" end="1836000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle39"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>要是你们敢对梅利号做什么</b></font></p>
<p begin="1836000000t" end="1867000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle40"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>我的8000人部下可不会放过你们的</b></font></p>
<p begin="1867000000t" end="1889000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle41"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>听到了吗 你这个泳裤混蛋</b></font></p>
<p begin="1891000000t" end="1915000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle42"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>小看我的话 可有你们受的</b></font></p>
<p begin="1917000000t" end="1963000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle43"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>令人恐惧的东海王者 乌索普船长就是我</b></font></p>
<p begin="1971000000t" end="1985000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle44"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>烦死人了</b></font></p>
<p begin="1990000000t" end="2005000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle45"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>少碰我你这混蛋...</b></font></p>
<p begin="2005000000t" end="2020000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle46"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>安静点</b></font></p>
<p begin="2031000000t" end="2044000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle47"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>好疼...</b></font></p>
<p begin="2044000000t" end="2056000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle48"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>对不起</b></font></p>
<p begin="2059000000t" end="2078000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle49"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>对不起 对不起啦</b></font></p>
<p begin="2096000000t" end="2143000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle50"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>这船已经不行了 Galley-La的检定没错</b></font></p>
<p begin="2149000000t" end="2185000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle51"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>身为解体屋 我劝你还是拆了吧</b></font></p>
<p begin="2192000000t" end="2217000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle52"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>你...开什么玩笑</b></font></p>
<p begin="2219000000t" end="2260000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle53"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>干脆就让我帮你拆了它吧</b></font></p>
<p begin="2260000000t" end="2289000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle54"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>什么 你说什么</b></font></p>
<p begin="2305000000t" end="2319000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle55"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>等等 你想干什么</b></font></p>
<p begin="2328000000t" end="2339000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle56"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>住手</b></font></p>
<p begin="2341000000t" end="2350000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle57"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>大哥</b></font></p>
<p begin="2354000000t" end="2392000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle58"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>我说了要帮你拆了这艘船啊</b></font></p>
<p begin="2392000000t" end="2404000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle59"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>少开玩笑了</b></font></p>
<p begin="2407000000t" end="2429000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle60"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>我才不会让你乱来的</b></font></p>
<p begin="2433000000t" end="2458000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle61"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>梅利号可是我的船</b></font></p>
<p begin="2461000000t" end="2471000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle62"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>不</b></font></p>
<p begin="2477000000t" end="2515000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle63"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>已经不是船了</b></font></p>
<p begin="2537000000t" end="2547000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle64"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>你说什么</b></font></p>
<p begin="2551000000t" end="2573990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle65"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>刚才我都问过你了</b></font></p>
<p begin="2575000000t" end="2598990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle66"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>你修船要做什么</b></font></p>
<p begin="2611000000t" end="2688000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle67"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>你要和它一起出海送死的话 我倒不会说什么</b></font></p>
<p begin="2700000000t" end="2755000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle68"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>不过你说想要用这艘船回东海的话</b></font></p>
<p begin="2761000000t" end="2798000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle69"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>我可就要阻止你了 小哥</b></font></p>
<p begin="2823000000t" end="2870000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle70"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>这艘船连下一个岛都去不了的</b></font></p>
<p begin="2879000000t" end="2889000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle71"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>听好了</b></font></p>
<p begin="2891000000t" end="2944000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle72"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>所谓船 就是要将人从一个海岸带到另一个海岸</b></font></p>
<p begin="2950000000t" end="2977000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle73"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>船就是为了达成这个约定而生的</b></font></p>
<p begin="2982000000t" end="3027000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle74"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>也就是说 无法将人带到另一个海岸的船...</b></font></p>
<p begin="3063000000t" end="3086000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle75"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>快住手</b></font></p>
<p begin="3096000000t" end="3148000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle76"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>无法到达下一个海岸的船 根本就不算船了啊</b></font></p>
<p begin="3161000000t" end="3172000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle77"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>大哥</b></font></p>
<p begin="3242000000t" end="3285000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle78"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>给我住手</b></font></p>
<p begin="4407900000t" end="4497100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle79"><font face="微软雅黑" size="32"><b>被船所爱的人!<br />乌索普的眼泪!</b></font></p>
<p begin="4581000000t" end="4618000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle80"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>你这混蛋给我离梅利远点儿</b></font></p>
<p begin="4730000000t" end="4755000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle81"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>你小子...</b></font></p>
<p begin="4774000000t" end="4792000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle82"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>还不明白的话</b></font></p>
<p begin="4847000000t" end="4896000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle83"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>就自己亲眼好好看看吧</b></font></p>
<p begin="6860000000t" end="6876000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle84"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>对不起 梅利</b></font></p>
<p begin="6925000000t" end="6954000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>我这就把你修好 把你修好</b></font></p>
<p begin="6963000000t" end="7023000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>我...不管多少次...多少次...</b></font></p>
<p begin="7026000000t" end="7043000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>也要修好你</b></font></p>
<p begin="7054000000t" end="7067000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>无论多少次都要...</b></font></p>
<p begin="7113000000t" end="7141000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>你给我适可而止 长鼻子</b></font></p>
<p begin="7145000000t" end="7159000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>你看到船底了吧</b></font></p>
<p begin="7164000000t" end="7196000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>折断的龙骨周围 外板也错位了</b></font></p>
<p begin="7198000000t" end="7211000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>肋骨也已破烂不堪</b></font></p>
<p begin="7214000000t" end="7250000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>这样的船身 只要一个浪打过来就会彻底散架</b></font></p>
<p begin="7254000000t" end="7288000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>像你这种外行人 随便缝缝补补根本就...</b></font></p>
<p begin="7375000000t" end="7396000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle95"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>你烦不烦啊</b></font></p>
<p begin="7399000000t" end="7421000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle96"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>你给我闭上嘴好不好</b></font></p>
<p begin="7426000000t" end="7461000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle97"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>再说话我就打飞你这个流氓</b></font></p>
<p begin="7706000000t" end="7718000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle98"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>其实...</b></font></p>
<p begin="7747000000t" end="7777000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle99"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>我...我知道的...</b></font></p>
<p begin="7799000000t" end="7812000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle100"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>你说什么</b></font></p>
<p begin="7823000000t" end="7917000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle101"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>其实...其实...</b></font></p>
<p begin="7924000000t" end="7939000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle102"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>我全都知道的</b></font></p>
<p begin="7966000000t" end="7992000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle103"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>我...我...</b></font></p>
<p begin="8016000000t" end="8066000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle104"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>早就知道梅利已经不行了</b></font></p>
<p begin="8309000000t" end="8320000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle105"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>我...</b></font></p>
<p begin="8336000000t" end="8366000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle106"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>其实...早就知道了...</b></font></p>
<p begin="8385000000t" end="8404000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle107"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>当我听到检定的结果时</b></font></p>
<p begin="8417000000t" end="8463000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle108"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>我就确定那天看到的事是真的</b></font></p>
<p begin="8480000000t" end="8510000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle109"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>一开始还以为是做梦</b></font></p>
<p begin="8516000000t" end="8542000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle110"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>一直认为怎么会有那种事</b></font></p>
<p begin="8565000000t" end="8575000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle111"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>我在某夜</b></font></p>
<p begin="8585000000t" end="8606000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle112"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>在大雾弥漫的月夜森林中</b></font></p>
<p begin="8616000000t" end="8641000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle113"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>听到了木槌敲打的声音</b></font></p>
<p begin="8652000000t" end="8695000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle114"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>那是从这艘本应无人的船上听到的</b></font></p>
<p begin="8707000000t" end="8768000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle115"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>是从受了重创 被当做祭品的船上传来的</b></font></p>
<p begin="8780000000t" end="8841000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle116"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>雾是很大 但那里的确有人在敲着木槌</b></font></p>
<p begin="8847000000t" end="8885000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle117"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>还有...虽然不知道是谁</b></font></p>
<p begin="8908000000t" end="8921000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle118"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>好棒啊</b></font></p>
<p begin="8910000000t" end="8934000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle119"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>但是第二天早上天亮时</b></font></p>
<p begin="8940000000t" end="8969000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle120"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>我们发现船被笨拙地修好了</b></font></p>
<p begin="8979000000t" end="9003000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle121"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>连断了的桅杆也修得和原来一模一样</b></font></p>
<p begin="9006000000t" end="9036000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle122"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>但是我更搞不懂的是</b></font></p>
<p begin="9054000000t" end="9102000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle123"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>为什么修船的人会知道梅利号原来的样子呢</b></font></p>
<p begin="9114000000t" end="9178000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle124"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>明明我们把船改造成那样 却还能将梅利恢复成原来的模样</b></font></p>
<p begin="9212000000t" end="9264000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle125"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>虽然一切都很不可思议 但总觉得有人在我心里留下了话</b></font></p>
<p begin="9276000000t" end="9291000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle126"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>虽然不知道是不是他直接跟我说的</b></font></p>
<p begin="9300000000t" end="9321000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle127"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>也许只是我的错觉</b></font></p>
<p begin="9342000000t" end="9352000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle128"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>放心吧</b></font></p>
<p begin="9384000000t" end="9408000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle129"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>我还会再载你们一段时间的</b></font></p>
<p begin="9436000000t" end="9456000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle130"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>也许听起来很荒谬</b></font></p>
<p begin="9461000000t" end="9534000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle131"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>可是我...我一直都认为那就是梅利号的化身</b></font></p>
<p begin="9583000000t" end="9623000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle132"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>船那时候一定已经到了极限</b></font></p>
<p begin="9628000000t" end="9679000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle133"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>可能是想让我们知道这些才以那种姿态出现的吧</b></font></p>
<p begin="9702000000t" end="9743000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle134"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>我听到检定的结果后 就是这么想的</b></font></p>
<p begin="9782000000t" end="9801000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle135"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>你一定认为我这人简直疯了吧</b></font></p>
<p begin="9807000000t" end="9824000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle136"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>你信不信无所谓</b></font></p>
<p begin="9851000000t" end="9860000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle137"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>大哥?</b></font></p>
<p begin="9873000000t" end="9892000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle138"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>不管我信不信</b></font></p>
<p begin="9897000000t" end="9946000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle139"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>你看到的是一个拿着木槌像船员一样的家伙吧</b></font></p>
<p begin="9957000000t" end="9981000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle140"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>你怎么会知道</b></font></p>
<p begin="9996000000t" end="10040000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle141"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>我说小哥 你可是看到船精灵了啊</b></font></p>
<p begin="10048000000t" end="10074000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle142"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>船精...</b></font></p>
<p begin="10079000000t" end="10095000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle143"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>船精灵</b></font></p>
<p begin="10102000000t" end="10130000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle144"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>是船员们世代相传的传说</b></font></p>
<p begin="10141000000t" end="10184000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle145"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>是只有真正被珍惜的船上才会寄宿的妖精</b></font></p>
<p begin="10191000000t" end="10213000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle146"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>换句话说就是船的化身</b></font></p>
<p begin="10232000000t" end="10268000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle147"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>手里拿着木槌 穿着船员的雨衣</b></font></p>
<p begin="10275000000t" end="10322000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle148"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>船遇险时 他会在船内到处奔跑传达给船员</b></font></p>
<p begin="10330000000t" end="10369000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle149"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>时常能够给予船员们很大的帮助</b></font></p>
<p begin="10372000000t" end="10415990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle150"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>说实话我还是第一次听说有人见过他</b></font></p>
<p begin="10435000000t" end="10475990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle151"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>正因为你们珍惜船 船才会感谢船员</b></font></p>
<p begin="10487000000t" end="10534000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle152"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>这艘船无论如何 一定也想将你们载到另一个海岸吧</b></font></p>
<p begin="10543000000t" end="10626000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle153"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>不惜以人的姿态出现 与他想搭载的船员见面</b></font></p>
<p begin="10633000000t" end="10661000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle154"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>这艘船也真是幸福啊</b></font></p>
<p begin="10716000000t" end="10728000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle155"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>梅利...</b></font></p>
<p begin="10792000000t" end="10821000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle156"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>是吗 那么果然...</b></font></p>
<p begin="10830000000t" end="10881000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle157"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>那时候和我说话的就是你啊</b></font></p>
<p begin="10893000000t" end="10903000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle158"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>梅利...</b></font></p>
<p begin="11006000000t" end="11033000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle159"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>不过还真是令人惊讶呢</b></font></p>
<p begin="11038000000t" end="11101000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle160"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>那么说你本来已知道船的真实情况还和伙伴吵了一架吗</b></font></p>
<p begin="11127000000t" end="11150000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle161"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>因为我无法如此轻易地下结论</b></font></p>
<p begin="11156000000t" end="11187000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle162"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>男人真是笨啊</b></font></p>
<p begin="11187000000t" end="11213000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle163"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>真笨啊</b></font></p>
<p begin="11295000000t" end="11312000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle164"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>好像有人来访</b></font></p>
<p begin="11328000000t" end="11344000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle165"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>那还能有谁啊</b></font></p>
<p begin="11345000000t" end="11363000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle166"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>肯定是赞拜他们吧</b></font></p>
<p begin="11374000000t" end="11405000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle167"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>话说他们为什么还要特地从海那边的门进来啊</b></font></p>
<p begin="11410000000t" end="11423000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle168"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>也是啊</b></font></p>
<p begin="11431000000t" end="11454000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle169"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>通常总是从上面的入口进来的</b></font></p>
<p begin="11458000000t" end="11484000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle170"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>搞不好他们带草帽小子来了呢</b></font></p>
<p begin="11488000000t" end="11539000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle171"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>对了<br />我都忘了是要将你当成诱饵 把草帽小子他们引来的</b></font></p>
<p begin="11545000000t" end="11594000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle172"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>他才不会来 都说了我们已经不是伙伴了</b></font></p>
<p begin="11658000000t" end="11679000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle173"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>干嘛不进来呢</b></font></p>
<p begin="11694000000t" end="11719000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle174"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>来了来了 马上开门</b></font></p>
<p begin="11740000000t" end="11767000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle175"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>来了来了 烦死了</b></font></p>
<p begin="11821000000t" end="11854000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle176"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>小哥 你还是回伙伴身边去吧</b></font></p>
<p begin="11883000000t" end="11902000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle177"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>现在已经不可能了</b></font></p>
<p begin="11904000000t" end="11924000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle178"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>我都已经和船长决斗过了</b></font></p>
<p begin="11927000000t" end="11954000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle179"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>而且船的事也还没有解决</b></font></p>
<p begin="11973000000t" end="11992000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle180"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>还谈什么解决啊</b></font></p>
<p begin="11998000000t" end="12047000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle181"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>既然知道船已经无法航行 那事情就好办多了</b></font></p>
<p begin="12089000000t" end="12103000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle182"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>就放我这儿吧</b></font></p>
<p begin="12110000000t" end="12140000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle183"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>我会处理掉你尽管放心</b></font></p>
<p begin="12143000000t" end="12189000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle184"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>就像刚才那样 这可是完全为你着想啊</b></font></p>
<p begin="12191000000t" end="12211000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle185"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>所以要把船彻底拆掉</b></font></p>
<p begin="12211000000t" end="12237000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle186"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>别多管闲事 这是我自己的事</b></font></p>
<p begin="12237000000t" end="12292400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle187"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>我都帮你解决问题了 你应该感谢我才是</b></font></p>
<p begin="12251000000t" end="12263000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle188"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>是赞拜吗</b></font></p>
<p begin="12294000000t" end="12320000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle189"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>什么感谢啊 少开玩笑了</b></font></p>
<p begin="12334000000t" end="12351000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle190"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>你还不明白吗</b></font></p>
<p begin="12357000000t" end="12381000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle191"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>你这么做 对船来说可是最为难的</b></font></p>
<p begin="12383000000t" end="12427000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle192"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>这艘船如此喜欢你们 甚至以人的姿态出现</b></font></p>
<p begin="12428000000t" end="12463000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle193"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>如果某一天载着你们在大洋中沉没</b></font></p>
<p begin="12480000000t" end="12519000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle194"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>这艘船也会死不瞑目 悔恨万分的</b></font></p>
<p begin="12526000000t" end="12597000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle195"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>那要是你有个将要死去的伙伴<br />难道你就忍心说出“你就快乐地死去吧” 然后转身离开吗</b></font></p>
<p begin="12597000000t" end="12635000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle196"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>这根本是两码事吧</b></font></p>
<p begin="12635000000t" end="12665000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle197"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>都是一样的 情况就是如此</b></font></p>
<p begin="12666000000t" end="12688000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle198"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>真是个固执的家伙啊</b></font></p>
<p begin="12751000000t" end="12758000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle199"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>莫兹</b></font></p>
<p begin="12826000000t" end="12834000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle200"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>基维</b></font></p>
<p begin="12841000000t" end="12861000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle201"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>你们是谁</b></font></p>
<p begin="12883000000t" end="12907000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle202"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>抱歉打扰你们了</b></font></p>
<p begin="12938000000t" end="12977000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle203"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>因为这两位小姐不让我们进来</b></font></p>
<p begin="13028000000t" end="13046000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle204"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>Galley-La的秘书</b></font></p>
<p begin="13082000000t" end="13114000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle205"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>你们想干什么</b></font></p>
<p begin="13901000000t" end="13924000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle206"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>Galley-La 你们到底是...</b></font></p>
<p begin="13924000000t" end="13953000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle207"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>现在我们可是政府的谍报人员 卡特·福兰姆</b></font></p>
<p begin="13953000000t" end="13963000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle208"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>为什么你们会知道这个名字...</b></font></p>
<p begin="13963000000t" end="14005000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle209"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>传说中的修船工汤姆将某样东西交给了你</b></font></p>
<p begin="14011000000t" end="14051000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle210"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>那么就把你的秘密交出来吧</b></font></p>
<p begin="14055000000t" end="14068000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle211"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>次回ONEPIECE</b></font></p>
<p begin="14071000000t" end="14103000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle212"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>福兰奇的过去!<br />海列车的启程之日</b></font></p>
<p begin="14103000000t" end="14124000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle213"><font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>海贼王!我当定了!</b></font></p>
